ed from incident INC-042: 4 tasks are in In Progress state. Tasks without activity for extended periods should be reviewed.\",\n    \"linkedIncidentId\": \"INC-042\",\n    \"tags\": [\n      \"incident-response\",\n      \"tasks\",\n      \"stale\",\n      \"in-progress\"\n    ],\n    \"history\": [\n      {\n        \"ts\": \"2026-06-02T18:30:29.000Z\",\n        \"action\": \"created\",\n        \"actor\": \"system\",\n        \"details\": \"Auto-created from incident INC-042\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"ts\": \"2026-06-02T18:39:53.136Z\",\n        \"action\": \"started\",\n        \"actor\": \"monkey\",\n        \"details\": \"Status changed from triage to in_progress\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"ts\": \"2026-06-02T19:02:30.140772+00:00\",\n        \"action\": \"stalled\",\n        \"actor\": \"heartbeat\",\n        \"details\": \"Auto-reset to backlog: dispatched but no agent ever picked up the task. currentStep was \\\"None\\\" with no progress after 22min. Dispatcher-agent handoff gap.\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"lastActivity\": \"2026-06-02T18:39:53.136Z\",\n    \"lastUpdated\": \"2026-06-02T19:02:30.140772+00:00\",\n    \"currentStep\": null,\n    \"startedAt\": \"2026-06-02T18:39:53.136Z\",\n    \"progress\": 0,\n    \"stalledAt\": \"2026-06-02T19:02:30.140772+00:00\",\n    \"dispatchCount\": 0\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": \"task-mpwz0zii-2ort\",\n    \"title\": \"Move Incident ShortCut\",\n    \"assignee\": \"monkey\",\n    \"status\": \"backlog\",\n    \"priority\": \"P3\",\n    \"ts\": \"just now\",\n    \"note\": \"In the left hand panel. Move Incident link above Scheduler\\n\\nI.e should be\\n\\nTask\\nIncident\\nSchedular\\n\\nRather than\\n\\nTask \\nSchedular\\nIncident\",\n    \"history\": [\n      {\n        \"ts\": \"2026-06-02T18:28:38.730Z\",\n        \"action\": \"created\",\n        \"actor\": \"monkey\",\n        \"details\": \"Task created\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"ts\": \"2026-06-02T18:28:42.210Z\",\n        \"action\": \"started\",\n 