{"type":"message","id":"7dde862d","parentId":"4ed00d6d","timestamp":"2026-06-03T19:03:18.923Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now update the NIGHT_SHIFT.md design doc to match:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"38f027d5-2291-4cb4-89ff-4bcfef4c0f23","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/NIGHT_SHIFT.md","edits":[{"oldText":"### Sub-agent Constraints\n- Each sub-agent gets a 15-minute timeout\n- Sub-agent must update `currentStep` and `lastActivity` every 5 min\n- Sub-agent must write a completion summary before marking done\n- If a sub-agent fails, the task goes back to backlog with failure note — no retry","newText":"### Sub-agent Constraints\n- Each sub-agent gets a 15-minute timeout\n- Sub-agent must update `currentStep` and `lastActivity` every 5 min — **this is non-negotiable for Night Shift**. The morning report will flag tasks that went straight from start→completion with no intermediate steps.\n- Sub-agent must write a completion summary before marking done\n- If a sub-agent fails, the task goes back to backlog with failure note — no retry\n- **Night Shift stall rule:** If a task has been in_progress for >30 min with no `lastActivity` update (or currentStep still \"Agent starting…\"), reset to backlog immediately. Never let a frozen task sit until morning."},{"oldText":"```\n🌙 Night Shift Report — [date]\n\n✅ Completed: X tasks\n⏭️ Skipped: Y tasks (rate limit / time / eligibility)\n❌ Failed: Z tasks\n🪙 Tokens used: ~N\n\nCompleted:\n• [Task title] — [one-line summary]\n• [Task title] — [one-line summary]\n\nFailed:\n• [Task title] — [reason]\n\n── Station Status ──\n💾 Disk: workspace X GB / MC repo Y GB\n🚨 Incidents overnight: [count + brief description, or \"None\"]\n⏱️ Gateway uptime: Xh Ym\n📊 Backlog remaining: N tasks (M night-shift eligible)\n```\n\nIf zero tasks were completed:\n\n```\n🟥 Night Shift Report — [date]\n\nNo tasks completed.\nReason: [no eligible tasks / rate limits hit / etc.]\n\n── Station Status ──\n💾 Disk: workspace X GB / MC repo Y GB\n🚨 Incidents overnight: [count + brief description, or \"None\"]\n⏱️ Gateway uptime: Xh Ym\n📊 Backlog: N tasks (0 night-shift eligible)\n```","newText":"```\n🌙 Night Shift Report — [date]\n\n✅ Completed: X tasks\n⏭️ Skipped: Y tasks (rate limit / time / eligibility)\n❌ Failed: Z tasks\n🪙 Tokens used: ~N\n\nCompleted:\n• [Task title] — [one-line summary]\n  ↳ Progress updates: [N] intermediate steps logged — [good/needs improvement]\n\n── Agent Behavior ──\n📈 Tasks with intermediate progress updates: X/Y\n⚠️ Tasks that went straight start→complete with no steps: [list or \"None\"]\n\n── Station Status ──\n💾 Disk: workspace X GB / MC repo Y GB\n🚨 Incidents overnight: [count + brief description, or \"None\"]\n⏱️ Gateway uptime: Xh Ym\n📊 Backlog remaining: N tasks (M night-shift eligible)\n```\n\nIf zero tasks were completed:\n\n```\n🟥 Night Shift Report — [date]\n\nNo tasks completed.\nReason: [no eligible tasks / rate limits hit / etc.]\n\n── Station Status ──\n💾 Disk: workspace X GB / MC repo Y GB\n🚨 Incidents overnight: [count + brief description, or \"None\"]\n⏱️ Gateway uptime: Xh Ym\n📊 Backlog: N tasks (0 night-shift eligible)\n```\n\n**Progress update assessment:** For each completed task, check its history. If there are no `progress` or `step_update` entries between `started` and `completed`, flag it. The goal is at least 2-3 intermediate updates per task."}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/NIGHT_SHIFT.md\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\": \"### Sub-agent Constraints\\n- Each sub-agent gets a 15-minute timeout\\n- Sub-agent must update `currentStep` and `lastActivity` every 5 min\\n- Sub-agent must write a completion summary before marking done\\n- If a sub-agent fails, the task goes back to backlog with failure note — no retry\", \"newText\": \"### Sub-agent Constraints\\n- Each sub-agent gets a 15-minute timeout\\n- Sub-agent must update `currentStep` and `lastActivity` every 5 min — **this is non-negotiable for Night Shift**. The morning report will flag tasks that went straight from start→completion with no intermediate steps.\\n- Sub-agent must write a completion summary before marking done\\n- If a sub-agent fails, the task goes back to backlog with failure note — no retry\\n- **Night Shift stall rule:** If a task has been in_progress for >30 min with no `lastActivity` update (or currentStep still \\\"Agent starting…\\\"), reset to backlog immediately. Never let a frozen task sit until morning.\"}, {\"oldText\": \"```\\n🌙 Night Shift Report — [date]\\n\\n✅ Completed: X tasks\\n⏭️ Skipped: Y tasks (rate limit / time / eligibility)\\n❌ Failed: Z tasks\\n🪙 Tokens used: ~N\\n\\nCompleted:\\n• [Task title] — [one-line summary]\\n• [Task title] — [one-line summary]\\n\\nFailed:\\n• [Task title] — [reason]\\n\\n── Station Status ──\\n💾 Disk: workspace X GB / MC repo Y GB\\n🚨 Incidents overnight: [count + brief description, or \\\"None\\\"]\\n⏱️ Gateway uptime: Xh Ym\\n📊 Backlog remaining: N tasks (M night-shift eligible)\\n```\\n\\nIf zero tasks were completed:\\n\\n```\\n🟥 Night Shift Report — [date]\\n\\nNo tasks completed.\\nReason: [no eligible tasks / rate limits hit / etc.]\\n\\n── Station Status ──\\n💾 Disk: workspace X GB / MC repo Y GB\\n🚨 Incidents overnight: [count + brief description, or \\\"None\\\"]\\n⏱️ Gateway uptime: Xh Ym\\n📊 Backlog: N tasks (0 night-shift eligible)\\n```\", \"newText\": \"```\\n🌙 Night Shift Report — [date]\\n\\n✅ Completed: X tasks\\n⏭️ Skipped: Y tasks (rate limit / time / eligibility)\\n❌ Failed: Z tasks\\n🪙 Tokens used: ~N\\n\\nCompleted:\\n• [Task title] — [one-line summary]\\n  ↳ Progress updates: [N] intermediate steps logged — [good/needs improvement]\\n\\n── Agent Behavior ──\\n📈 Tasks with intermediate progress updates: X/Y\\n⚠️ Tasks that went straight start→complete with no steps: [list or \\\"None\\\"]\\n\\n── Station Status ──\\n💾 Disk: workspace X GB / MC repo Y GB\\n🚨 Incidents overnight: [count + brief description, or \\\"None\\\"]\\n⏱️ Gateway uptime: Xh Ym\\n📊 Backlog remaining: N tasks (M night-shift eligible)\\n```\\n\\nIf zero tasks were completed:\\n\\n```\\n🟥 Night Shift Report — [date]\\n\\nNo tasks completed.\\nReason: [no eligible tasks / rate limits hit / etc.]\\n\\n── Station Status ──\\n💾 Disk: workspace X GB / MC repo Y GB\\n🚨 Incidents overnight: [count + brief description, or \\\"None\\\"]\\n⏱️ Gateway uptime: Xh Ym\\n📊 Backlog: N tasks (0 night-shift eligible)\\n```\\n\\n**Progress update assessment:** For each completed task, check its history. If there are no `progress` or `step_update` entries between `started` and `completed`, flag it. The goal is at least 2-3 intermediate updates per task.\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":784,"output":942,"cacheRead":105088,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":106814,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780513366105,"responseId":"gen-1780513366-9MHmON2NDMlJKD99WImI"}}
{"type":"message","id":"06556b50","parentId":"7dde862d","timestamp":"2026-06-03T19:03:18.948Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"38f027d5-2291-4cb4-89ff-4bcfef4c0f23","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 2 block(s) in /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/NIGHT_SHIFT.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 105 - Never dispatch P1 tasks at night\n 106 \n 107 ### Sub-agent Constraints\n 108 - Each sub-agent gets a 15-minute timeout\n-109 - Sub-agent must update `currentStep` and `lastActivity` every 5 min\n+109 - Sub-agent must update `currentStep` and `lastActivity` every 5 min — **this is non-negotiable for Night Shift**. The morning report will flag tasks that went straight from start→completion with no intermediate steps.\n 110 - Sub-agent must write a completion summary before marking done\n 111 - If a sub-agent fails, the task goes back to backlog with failure note — no retry\n+112 - **Night Shift stall rule:** If a task has been in_progress for >30 min with no `lastActivity` update (or currentStep still \"Agent starting…\"), reset to backlog immediately. Never let a frozen task sit until morning.\n 112 \n 113 ---\n 114 \n 115 ## 5. State Persistence\n     ...\n 151 🪙 Tokens used: ~N\n 152 \n 153 Completed:\n 154 • [Task title] — [one-line summary]\n-155 • [Task title] — [one-line summary]\n+156   ↳ Progress updates: [N] intermediate steps logged — [good/needs improvement]\n 156 \n-157 Failed:\n-158 • [Task title] — [reason]\n+158 ── Agent Behavior ──\n+159 📈 Tasks with intermediate progress updates: X/Y\n+160 ⚠️ Tasks that went straight start→complete with no steps: [list or \"None\"]\n 159 \n 160 ── Station Status ──\n 161 💾 Disk: workspace X GB / MC repo Y GB\n 162 🚨 Incidents overnight: [count + brief description, or \"None\"]\n     ...\n 178 ⏱️ Gateway uptime: Xh Ym\n 179 📊 Backlog: N tasks (0 night-shift eligible)\n 180 ```\n 181 \n+184 **Progress update assessment:** For each completed task, check its history. If there are no `progress` or `step_update` entries between `started` and `completed`, flag it. The goal is at least 2-3 intermediate updates per task.\n+185 \n 182 ---\n 183 \n 184 ## 7. Risks and Mitigations\n 185 \n     ...","patch":"--- /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/NIGHT_SHIFT.md\n+++ /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/NIGHT_SHIFT.md\n@@ -105,11 +105,12 @@\n - Never dispatch P1 tasks at night\n \n ### Sub-agent Constraints\n - Each sub-agent gets a 15-minute timeout\n-- Sub-agent must update `currentStep` and `lastActivity` every 5 min\n+- Sub-agent must update `currentStep` and `lastActivity` every 5 min — **this is non-negotiable for Night Shift**. The morning report will flag tasks that went straight from start→completion with no intermediate steps.\n - Sub-agent must write a completion summary before marking done\n - If a sub-agent fails, the task goes back to backlog with failure note — no retry\n+- **Night Shift stall rule:** If a task has been in_progress for >30 min with no `lastActivity` update (or currentStep still \"Agent starting…\"), reset to backlog immediately. Never let a frozen task sit until morning.\n \n ---\n \n ## 5. State Persistence\n@@ -151,12 +152,13 @@\n 🪙 Tokens used: ~N\n \n Completed:\n • [Task title] — [one-line summary]\n-• [Task title] — [one-line summary]\n+  ↳ Progress updates: [N] intermediate steps logged — [good/needs improvement]\n \n-Failed:\n-• [Task title] — [reason]\n+── Agent Behavior ──\n+📈 Tasks with intermediate progress updates: X/Y\n+⚠️ Tasks that went straight start→complete with no steps: [list or \"None\"]\n \n ── Station Status ──\n 💾 Disk: workspace X GB / MC repo Y GB\n 🚨 Incidents overnight: [count + brief description, or \"None\"]\n@@ -178,8 +180,10 @@\n ⏱️ Gateway uptime: Xh Ym\n 📊 Backlog: N tasks (0 night-shift eligible)\n ```\n \n+**Progress update assessment:** For each completed task, check its history. If there are no `progress` or `step_update` entries between `started` and `completed`, flag it. The goal is at least 2-3 intermediate updates per task.\n+\n ---\n \n ## 7. Risks and Mitigations\n \n","firstChangedLine":109},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780513398947}}
{"type":"message","id":"2315c1bc","parentId":"06556b50","timestamp":"2026-06-03T19:03:43.152Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me also make the sub-agent spawn template even more explicit about intermediate updates. The key issue is that sub-agents need to run the Python update script at every step, not just at start and end. Let me update the task brief template in HEARTBEAT.md:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"94dca5af-c1fc-4dae-9a64-e6d22aca4333","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md","edits":[{"oldText":"### Dispatch\n- Pick ONE eligible task, spawn sub-agent with full task brief\n- Sub-agent MUST update `currentStep` and `lastActivity` every 5-10 min — this is CRITICAL. Without intermediate updates, stall detection cannot function and the morning report cannot assess agent behavior.\n- **Night Shift stall rule:** If a task has been in_progress for >30 min with no `lastActivity` update (or currentStep still shows \"Agent starting…\"), reset it to backlog immediately. Do NOT let Night Shift tasks sit frozen. The 07:00 morning report should never show a task that's been stuck for hours.\n- On completion: mark done with summary, pick next eligible task\n- On failure: move back to backlog with failure note, no retry\n- Stop immediately if 429s detected or Andre sends a message","newText":"### Dispatch\n- Pick ONE eligible task, spawn sub-agent with full task brief\n- Sub-agent MUST update `currentStep` and `lastActivity` every 5-10 min — this is CRITICAL. Without intermediate updates, stall detection cannot function and the morning report cannot assess agent behavior.\n- **Night Shift stall rule:** If a task has been in_progress for >30 min with no `lastActivity` update (or currentStep still shows \"Agent starting…\"), reset it to backlog immediately. Do NOT let Night Shift tasks sit frozen. The 07:00 morning report should never show a task that's been stuck for hours.\n- On completion: mark done with summary, pick next eligible task\n- On failure: move back to backlog with failure note, no retry\n- Stop immediately if 429s detected or Andre sends a message\n- **Night Shift sub-agent brief MUST include:**\n  - The exact Python script to update tasks.json at every step (copy from Task Pickup section)\n  - Explicit instruction: \"Run the update script after EVERY file read, edit, test, or decision — not just at start and completion\"\n  - Warning: \"The morning report will flag tasks with no intermediate progress updates\""}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\": \"### Dispatch\\n- Pick ONE eligible task, spawn sub-agent with full task brief\\n- Sub-agent MUST update `currentStep` and `lastActivity` every 5-10 min — this is CRITICAL. Without intermediate updates, stall detection cannot function and the morning report cannot assess agent behavior.\\n- **Night Shift stall rule:** If a task has been in_progress for >30 min with no `lastActivity` update (or currentStep still shows \\\"Agent starting…\\\"), reset it to backlog immediately. Do NOT let Night Shift tasks sit frozen. The 07:00 morning report should never show a task that's been stuck for hours.\\n- On completion: mark done with summary, pick next eligible task\\n- On failure: move back to backlog with failure note, no retry\\n- Stop immediately if 429s detected or Andre sends a message\", \"newText\": \"### Dispatch\\n- Pick ONE eligible task, spawn sub-agent with full task brief\\n- Sub-agent MUST update `currentStep` and `lastActivity` every 5-10 min — this is CRITICAL. Without intermediate updates, stall detection cannot function and the morning report cannot assess agent behavior.\\n- **Night Shift stall rule:** If a task has been in_progress for >30 min with no `lastActivity` update (or currentStep still shows \\\"Agent starting…\\\"), reset it to backlog immediately. Do NOT let Night Shift tasks sit frozen. The 07:00 morning report should never show a task that's been stuck for hours.\\n- On completion: mark done with summary, pick next eligible task\\n- On failure: move back to backlog with failure note, no retry\\n- Stop immediately if 429s detected or Andre sends a message\\n- **Night Shift sub-agent brief MUST include:**\\n  - The exact Python script to update tasks.json at every step (copy from Task Pickup section)\\n  - Explicit instruction: \\\"Run the update script after EVERY file read, edit, test, or decision — not just at start and completion\\\"\\n  - Warning: \\\"The morning report will flag tasks with no intermediate progress updates\\\"\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":997,"output":553,"cacheRead":105856,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":107406,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780513398954,"responseId":"gen-1780513399-EvifBeMMl0BvVvIn4y54"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e0a84aa7","parentId":"2315c1bc","timestamp":"2026-06-03T19:03:43.176Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"94dca5af-c1fc-4dae-9a64-e6d22aca4333","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n  83 - **Night Shift stall rule:** If a task has been in_progress for >30 min with no `lastActivity` update (or currentStep still shows \"Agent starting…\"), reset it to backlog immediately. Do NOT let Night Shift tasks sit frozen. The 07:00 morning report should never show a task that's been stuck for hours.\n  84 - On completion: mark done with summary, pick next eligible task\n  85 - On failure: move back to backlog with failure note, no retry\n  86 - Stop immediately if 429s detected or Andre sends a message\n+ 87 - **Night Shift sub-agent brief MUST include:**\n+ 88   - The exact Python script to update tasks.json at every step (copy from Task Pickup section)\n+ 89   - Explicit instruction: \"Run the update script after EVERY file read, edit, test, or decision — not just at start and completion\"\n+ 90   - Warning: \"The morning report will flag tasks with no intermediate progress updates\"\n  87 \n  88 ### Forbidden\n  89 - Never modify openclaw.json, cron jobs, LaunchAgents, or gateway config\n  90 - Never delete tasks — only move to Done with summary\n     ...","patch":"--- /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\n+++ /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\n@@ -83,8 +83,12 @@\n - **Night Shift stall rule:** If a task has been in_progress for >30 min with no `lastActivity` update (or currentStep still shows \"Agent starting…\"), reset it to backlog immediately. Do NOT let Night Shift tasks sit frozen. The 07:00 morning report should never show a task that's been stuck for hours.\n - On completion: mark done with summary, pick next eligible task\n - On failure: move back to backlog with failure note, no retry\n - Stop immediately if 429s detected or Andre sends a message\n+- **Night Shift sub-agent brief MUST include:**\n+  - The exact Python script to update tasks.json at every step (copy from Task Pickup section)\n+  - Explicit instruction: \"Run the update script after EVERY file read, edit, test, or decision — not just at start and completion\"\n+  - Warning: \"The morning report will flag tasks with no intermediate progress updates\"\n \n ### Forbidden\n - Never modify openclaw.json, cron jobs, LaunchAgents, or gateway config\n - Never delete tasks — only move to Done with summary\n","firstChangedLine":87},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780513423175}}
