{"type":"message","id":"0f0d8939","parentId":"e3badf3f","timestamp":"2026-06-03T19:07:17.306Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me start processing. The highest priority task is `task-fd625713` \"Incident → Task Linking\" (P1). But wait — this is a planning/design task from the strategic backlog. Let me re-read Andre's rules: work on it, and if it's blocked/unclear, move to Triage. Let me pick it up and assess:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"fa07984b-3b60-4303-88da-d9e4c7a90dd5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\n\ntasks_file = \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/data/tasks.json\"\nwith open(tasks_file) as f:\n    tasks = json.load(f)\n\nnow = datetime.now(timezone.utc)\n\n# Pick up the P1 task\nfor t in tasks:\n    if t['id'] == 'task-fd625713':\n        t['status'] = 'in_progress'\n        t['currentStep'] = 'Assessing task requirements and existing codebase'\n        t['progress'] = 5\n        t['lastActivity'] = now.isoformat()\n        t['startedAt'] = now.isoformat()\n        t.pop('stalledAt', None)\n        if 'history' not in t:\n            t['history'] = []\n        t['history'].append({\n            'ts': now.isoformat(),\n            'action': 'started',\n            'actor': 'monkey',\n            'details': 'Picked up for backlog processing — assessing feasibility'\n        })\n        print(f\"Picked up: {t['title']}\")\n        print(f\"Note: {t.get('note','')[:300]}\")\n        break\n\nwith open(tasks_file, 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(tasks, f, indent=2)\nPYEOF","timeout":5},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"python3 << 'PYEOF'\\nimport json\\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\\n\\ntasks_file = \\\"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/data/tasks.json\\\"\\nwith open(tasks_file) as f:\\n    tasks = json.load(f)\\n\\nnow = datetime.now(timezone.utc)\\n\\n# Pick up the P1 task\\nfor t in tasks:\\n    if t['id'] == 'task-fd625713':\\n