{"type":"message","id":"282f1c43","parentId":"c0d4234a","timestamp":"2026-06-03T19:33:49.804Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"6f10c518-59b2-45e3-8fa2-cae0d2e1098c","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/FRAMEWORK.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n  11 ### Mission Control Dashboard\n  12 - **Stack:** TanStack Start + React + Vite + Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui\n  13 - **Runtime:** Bun\n  14 - **Repo:** `~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/`\n- 15 - **Branch strategy:** `main` = prod (port 3000), `dev` = dev (port 3001)\n+ 15 - **Branch strategy:** `main` is the single branch, served on port 3000. No dev branch.\n  16 - **Correct sources:** See `SOURCES.md` → \"TanStack Start Project\"\n  17 \n  18 ---\n  19 \n     ...","patch":"--- /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/FRAMEWORK.md\n+++ /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/FRAMEWORK.md\n@@ -11,9 +11,9 @@\n ### Mission Control Dashboard\n - **Stack:** TanStack Start + React + Vite + Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui\n - **Runtime:** Bun\n - **Repo:** `~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/`\n-- **Branch strategy:** `main` = prod (port 3000), `dev` = dev (port 3001)\n+- **Branch strategy:** `main` is the single branch, served on port 3000. No dev branch.\n - **Correct sources:** See `SOURCES.md` → \"TanStack Start Project\"\n \n ---\n \n","firstChangedLine":15},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780515229803}}
