{"type":"message","id":"f7a60dcf","parentId":"a4f8c503","timestamp":"2026-06-03T21:35:23.691Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Report\n\n**Andre's triage decisions applied:**\n\n| # | Task | Action |\n|---|------|--------|\n| 1 | Unified Event Model + Incident Events | ✅ Merged into \"Timeline — Unified Event Model\" → **Done** |\n| 2 | Automation Health States | → Backlog (P2, clarified scope) |\n| 3 | Retry Policies | → Backlog (P2, clarified scope) |\n| 4 | Runbook Evolution | → Backlog (P3, depends on Phase 2 Runbooks) |\n| 5 | Incident Response Atmosphere | → Backlog (P3, clarified scope) |\n| 6 | Operational Readiness Dashboard | → Backlog (P2, clarified scope) |\n\n**What was built this session (8 tasks total):**\n\n| # | Task | Status |\n|---|------|--------|\n| 1 | Incident → Task Linking | ✅ Done (already implemented) |\n| 2 | Runbook Data Model | ✅ Done (runbooks.ts, 5 runbooks) |\n| 3 | Runbook UI | ✅ Done (IncidentDetailsDrawer panel) |\n| 4 | Incident Type Mapping | ✅ Done (classifyIncident + suggestRunbook) |\n| 5 | Task Creation From Runbooks | ✅ Done (incidents-create creates step tasks) |\n| 6 | Asset View | ✅ Done (/assets route + data model) |\n| 7 | Auto Remediation | ✅ Done (4 rules + /api/remediate) |\n| 8 | Timeline — Unified Event Model | ✅ Done (/timeline page + incident timeline) |\n\n**Backlog: 5 tasks remaining**\n- P2: Automation Health States, Retry Policies, Operational Readiness Dashboard\n- P3: Runbook Evolution (Phase 2 dep), Incident Response Atmosphere\n\n**Triage: 0** — all cleared."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":181,"output":404,"cacheRead":174464,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":175049,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780522507449,"responseId":"gen-1780522507-pAURLlUoFQkbHH8dEYvS"}}
