{"type":"message","id":"2713011f","parentId":"1db93ec2","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:23:08.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hmm, interesting — both processes are serving port 3000! The dev server on 3001 isn't actually running as a separate instance. Let me check what's really going on:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"99ab763a-33b5-462e-9718-4de99bf4e5f3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ps aux | grep vite | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2, $11, $12, $13, $14}'\necho \"---\"\n# Check if there's a separate dev server script or LaunchAgent\nls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/scripts/ 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\n# Check what's actually listening on 3001\nlsof -i :3001 2>/dev/null | head -5","timeout":10},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"ps aux | grep vite | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2, $11, $12, $13, $14}'\\necho \\\"---\\\"\\n# Check if there's a separate dev server script or LaunchAgent\\nls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/scripts/ 2>/dev/null\\necho \\\"---\\\"\\n# Check what's actually listening on 3001\\nlsof -i :3001 2>/dev/null | head -5\", \"timeout\": 10}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":521,"output":172,"cacheRead":18944,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":19637,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780501879934,"responseId":"gen-1780501880-oh2HWeJmcjF9IqJA6mIE"}}
{"type":"message","id":"506809af","parentId":"2713011f","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:23:08.223Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"99ab763a-33b5-462e-9718-4de99bf4e5f3","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[... 1085 more characters truncated; rerun with narrower args if need"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":79,"aggregated":"67081 node /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/node_modules/.bin/vite dev --host\n67077 node /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/node_modules/.bin/vite dev --host\n---\ntotal 216\ndrwx------@ 10 spacemonkey  staff    320 May 16 15:09 .\ndrwx------@ 32 spacemonkey  staff   1024 May 31 13:02 ..\n-rwx------@  1 spacemonkey  staff    767 May 15 10:17 dev-server.sh\n-rw-------@  1 spacemonkey  staff   1475 May 14 18:46 launch-on-login.sh\n-rw-------@  1 spacemonkey  staff   3954 May 15 17:02 render-new-assets.cjs\n-rw-------@  1 spacemonkey  staff  38794 May 15 17:02 rooms-new.html\n-rw-------@  1 spacemonkey  staff   1500 May 15 15:18 scale-4x.cjs\n-rw-------@  1 spacemonkey  staff   2364 May 15 15:18 scale-sprites.cjs\n-rw-------@  1 spacemonkey  staff  41107 May 15 16:58 sprites-new.html\n-rw-------@  1 spacemonkey  staff    345 May 28 09:57 start-mc.sh\n---\nCOMMAND   PID        USER   FD   TYPE             DEVICE SIZE/OFF NODE NAME\nnode    67081 spacemonkey   16u  IPv6 0xae69c84a4e00bf41      0t0  TCP *:redwood-broker (LISTEN)","cwd":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780501922365}}
{"type":"message","id":"6fb139aa","parentId":"506809af","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:23:08.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OK so there are **two Vite processes** but both are serving port **3000** (the second one, PID 67081, grabbed 3001 as an ephemeral port — \"redwood-broker\" is just the service name for 3001, but it's not intentionally serving the dev site there).\n\nThe curl to 3001 earlier was probably hitting a cached response or redirect. Let me verify:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"e9eb2d9c-ecb4-484a-abe0-176bbc3621cc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Actually check what 3001 serves\ncurl -s -I http://localhost:3001/ 2>/dev/null | head -5\necho \"===\"\n# And 3000\ncurl -s -I http://localhost:3000/ 2>/dev/null | head 5\necho \"===\"\n# Check git status on both branches\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard\necho \"main:\" && git log --oneline main -1\necho \"dev:\" && git log --oneline dev -1\necho \"---\"\ngit diff main dev --stat 2>/dev/null","timeout":10},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Actually check what 3001 serves\\ncurl -s -I http://localhost:3001/ 2>/dev/null | head -5\\necho \\\"===\\\"\\n# And 3000\\ncurl -s -I http://localhost:3000/ 2>/dev/null | head 5\\necho \\\"===\\\"\\n# Check git status on both branches\\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard\\necho \\\"main:\\\" && git log --oneline main -1\\necho \\\"dev:\\\" && git log --oneline dev -1\\necho \\\"---\\\"\\ngit diff main dev --stat 2>/dev/null\", \"timeout\": 10}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":652,"output":258,"cacheRead":19456,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":20366,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780501922367,"responseId":"gen-1780501922-yK0Zfv5k030GHdg3hD9k"}}
