{"type":"message","id":"ae8f2456","parentId":"edb1acd8","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:23:08.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OK, here's the deal:\n\n**We don't actually have two separate systems.** We have:\n\n- **One repo** (`mission-control-dashboard`) with two branches: `main` (prod) and `dev`\n- **Two Vite processes** but they're both serving on port 3000 — the second one just grabbed 3001 as an ephemeral port, it's not intentionally running a dev instance\n- The `dev` branch has **massive differences** from `main` — 125 files changed, ~8.4K lines removed, ~2.8K added. It looks like a huge refactor happened on dev that never got merged to main\n\nSo the dev/prod branch strategy we set up (main=3000, dev=3001) isn't really being used. There's no separate dev server running the dev branch.\n\n**What do you want to do?**\n\n1. **Merge dev → main** if that refactor is ready\n2. **Set up a proper dev server** on port 3001 running the dev branch (separate clone or separate Vite instance)\n3. **Clean up** — if the dev branch work is already stale, just delete it and keep main as the single source of truth\n\nWhat's the state of that dev branch — is that work you want to keep?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":2838,"output":292,"cacheRead":20096,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":23226,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780501975184,"responseId":"gen-1780501975-BZPZTSDEf6yWy3ZvYTmi"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b15dc69a","parentId":"ae8f2456","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:23:08.223Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"The dev branch is stale — it's from the Lovable prototype era. All real \nwork has been on main. Don't merge it.\n\n1. Delete the dev branch (locally and on GitHub)\n2. Kill the second Vite process on port 3001\n3. Main is the single source of truth — one branch, one dev server on \n   port 3000\n4. Update FRAMEWORK.md if it references a dev/prod branch strategy","timestamp":1780502721542,"idempotencyKey":"7199b798-307e-4635-b1f5-b839713b72e0:user"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5b341574","parentId":"b15dc69a","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:23:08.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGot it. Let's clean this up."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"50422cbd-4a8f-4226-8210-1b2e62583713","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard\n# Delete dev branch locally and on GitHub\ngit branch -d dev 2>/dev/null || git branch -D dev\ngit push origin --dev dev 2>/dev/null || git push origin --delete dev 2>/dev/null\necho \"---branches---\"\ngit branch -a","timeout":15},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard\\n# Delete dev branch locally and on GitHub\\ngit branch -d dev 2>/dev/null || git branch -D dev\\ngit push origin --dev dev 2>/dev/null || git push origin --delete dev 2>/dev/null\\necho \\\"---branches---\\\"\\ngit branch -a\", \"timeout\": 15}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"02238551-35c2-4778-8fc3-48dc3ecfe180","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Kill the stray Vite process\nps aux | grep vite | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2, $11, $12, $13, $14}'","timeout":5},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Kill the stray Vite process\\nps aux | grep vite | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2, $11, $12, $13, $14}'\", \"timeout\": 5}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"1e070ff3-a4a9-4fa8-a2f8-e392e76382a1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check FRAMEWORK.md for dev/prov branch references\ngrep -rn -i 'dev.*branch\\|prod.*branch\\|3001\\|dev.*prod\\|branch.*strategy\\|dev.*server' ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/FRAMEWORK.md 2>/dev/null || echo \"No FRAMEWORK.md or no matches\"","timeout":5},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Check FRAMEWORK.md for dev/prov branch references\\ngrep -rn -i 'dev.*branch\\\\|prod.*branch\\\\|3001\\\\|dev.*prod\\\\|branch.*strategy\\\\|dev.*server' ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/FRAMEWORK.md 2>/dev/null || echo \\\"No FRAMEWORK.md or no matches\\\"\", \"timeout\": 5}"},{"type":"t