{"type":"message","id":"bdb8fb4f","parentId":"9109ff72","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:23:08.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OK so the in_progress task has been sitting for **98 minutes** with `currentStep: \"Agent starting…\"` at 5%. That's well past the 30-minute warning threshold but not yet at the 2-hour auto-reset. But the real problem is clear: **no agent is actually working on this task**. It was auto-dispatched by the work-dispatcher script, which just flips the status to `in_progress` — it doesn't actually spawn an agent to do the work.\n\nLet me now do a thorough analysis and fix."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"5c54dd2b-c060-470a-89c5-faa5e62c73b2","name":"update_plan","arguments":{"plan":[{"step":"Diagnose the in_progress task stall","status":"completed"},{"step":"Reset the stalled task to backlog","status":"in_progress"},{"step":"Analyze root cause: dispatcher flips status but doesn't spawn agents","status":"pending"},{"step":"Fix the work-dispatcher to actually dispatch work","status":"pending"},{"step":"Update HEARTBEAT.md with corrected dispatch logic","status":"pending"},{"step":"Report findings to Andre","status":"pending"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"plan\": [{\"step\": \"Diagnose the in_progress task stall\", \"status\": \"completed\"}, {\"step\": \"Reset the stalled task to backlog\", \"status\": \"in_progress\"}, {\"step\": \"Analyze root cause: dispatcher flips status but doesn't spawn agents\", \"status\": \"pending\"}, {\"step\": \"Fix the work-dispatcher to actually dispatch work\", \"status\": \"pending\"}, {\"step\": \"Update HEARTBEAT.md with corrected dispatch logic\", \"status\": \"pending\"}, {\"step\": \"Report findings to Andre\", \"status\": \"pending\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":407,"output":249,"cacheRead":56192,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":56848,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0