{"type":"message","id":"10179f11","parentId":"ef435a2b","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:23:08.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me dispatch the test task. I'll spawn a sub-agent to do it:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"2f0b536a-69e2-43e2-8f80-efca2097ed6d","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"label":"move-incident-shortcut","mode":"run","task":"## Task: Move Incident ShortCut in Sidebar\n\n**Task ID:** task-mpwz0zii-2ort\n**Priority:** P3\n**Status:** backlog → in_progress\n\n### What to do\nIn the Mission Control Dashboard sidebar (left panel), move the \"Incident\" link above \"Scheduler\".\n\nCurrent order:\n1. Tasks\n2. Scheduler\n3. Incident\n\nShould be:\n1. Tasks\n2. Incident\n3. Scheduler\n\n### Where to look\n- The sidebar component is likely in `src/components/AppSidebar.tsx` or similar\n- The route definitions are in `src/routeTree.gen.ts` or the sidebar config\n- Look for the navigation items array/order\n\n### Steps\n1. Find the sidebar navigation definition\n2. Reorder so Incident comes before Scheduler\n3. Verify the app still loads (check `bun run dev` is running on port 3000)\n4. Commit with message: \"Reorder sidebar: Incident above Scheduler\"\n\n### Important\n- The dev server is already running on port 3000 — don't restart it\n- After making changes, Vite will hot-reload automatically\n- Verify by checking the sidebar in the browser\n\n### Update task progress\nAfter completing, update the task in `data/tasks.json`:\n- Set status to \"done\"\n- Set progress to 100\n- Set currentStep to \"Completed\"\n- Add a summary: \"Reordered sidebar navigation: Incident link now appears above Scheduler\"\n- Add history entry with action \"completed\""},"partialArgs":"{\"label\": \"move-incident-shortcut\", \"mode\": \"run\", \"task\": \"## Task: Move Incident ShortCut in Sidebar\\n\\n**Task ID:** task-mpwz0zii-2ort\\n**Priority:** P3\\n**Status:** backlog → in_progress\\n\\n### What to do\\nIn the Mission Control Dashboard sidebar (left panel), move the \\\"Incident\\\" link above \\\"Scheduler\\\".\\n\\nCurrent order:\\n1. Tasks\\n2. Scheduler\\n3. Incident\\n\\nShould be:\\n1. Tasks\\n2. Incident\\n3. Scheduler\\n\\n### Where to look\\n- The sidebar component is likely in `src/components/AppSidebar.tsx` or similar\\n- The route definitions are in `src/routeTree.gen.ts` or the sidebar config\\n- Look for the navigation items array/order\\n\\n### Steps\\n1. Find the sidebar navigation definition\\n2. Reorder so Incident comes before Scheduler\\n3. Verify the app still loads (check `bun run dev` is running on port 3000)\\n4. Commit with message: \\\"Reorder sidebar: Incident above Scheduler\\\"\\n\\n### Important\\n- The dev server is already running on port 3000 — don't restart it\\n- After making changes, Vite will hot-reload automatically\\n- Verify by checking the sidebar in the browser\\n\\n### Update task progress\\nAfter completing, update the task in `data/tasks.json`:\\n- Set status to \\\"done\\\"\\n- Set progress to 100\\n- Set currentStep to \\\"Completed\\\"\\n- Add a summary: \\\"Reordered sidebar navigation: Incident link now appears above Scheduler\\\"\\n- Add history entry with action \\\"completed\\\"\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":206,"output":376,"cacheRead":71680,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":72262,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780507322798,"responseId":"gen-1780507322-xhwW1K6jLzO68j0dVmOM"}}
