{"type":"message","id":"54b22225","parentId":"18f9db92","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:23:08.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All done. Here's the full summary:\n\n---\n\n## ✅ All 4 Steps Complete\n\n### 1. Work-Dispatcher Disabled\n- Script renamed to `work-dispatcher.sh.disabled` — can't accidentally run\n- No cron job or LaunchAgent was active (it was already dead)\n- **Heartbeat is now the only dispatcher**\n\n### 2. 28 Protected Tasks Cleaned Up\n- **6 stale incident/dispatch artifacts** → marked Done as \"Obsolete — cleaned up\"\n  - `[Dispatch] Apply standard fix`, `[Dispatch] Review and triage`, `[Dispatch] Investigate issue`\n  - `Investigate: INC-040`, `Investigate: INC-041`, `Investigate: INC-042`\n- **22 strategic planning tasks** → marked Done as \"Deferred — needs human design input\"\n  - Circuit Breakers, Asset Schema, Runbook Data Model, Priority/Severity System, etc.\n  - These are roadmap items that need your spec before an agent can build them\n- **Backlog now: 16 tasks** (down from 44), all dispatchable\n\n### 3. Heartbeat Dispatch Logic Verified\n- HEARTBEAT.md updated with clear dispatch rules (P1 first, one task per heartbeat, crew routing)\n- Stall detection tightened: \"Agent starting…\" after 30 min → immediate reset\n- No competing dispatchers\n\n### 4. End-to-End Test: ✅ PASSED\n- **Task:** \"Move Incident ShortCut\" — reorder sidebar items\n- **Dispatched:** Sub-agent spawned via `sessions_spawn`\n- **Result:** Completed in 4.5 minutes\n  - Found `AppSidebar.tsx`, swapped Scheduler/Incidents order\n  - Vite hot-reloaded, app verified 200 on port 3000\n  - Committed and pushed: `8064e65`\n  - Task auto-moved to Done with completion summary\n- **The task system works end-to-end** 🎉\n\n### Current State\n| Status | Count |\n|--------|-------|\n| Backlog | 16 |\n| In Progress | 0 |\n| Done | 66 |\n\nThe 16 backlog items are all planning/design tasks needing your input. Nothing will be auto-dispatched without you clearing it."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":145,"output":505,"cacheRead":73728,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":74378,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780507686871,"responseId":"gen-1780507686-yNRjaHcYaBLQ32KpRu73"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5edf215b","parentId":"54b22225","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:23:08.223Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"The task system is operational. The end-to-end test passed. \n\nNow: the 16 remaining backlog tasks are all planning/design items \nthat need my input before an agent can work on them. That's correct \n— they're the strategic roadmap items from Phase 1-6.\n\nGoing forward:\n1. I create tasks in Backlog when I want work done\n2. The heartbeat dispatches P1 tasks first, one at a time\n3. Agents update currentStep and progress while working\n4. Stall detection catches abandoned tasks at 30 min\n5. Completed tasks auto-move to Done with summaries\n\nNo more shell scripts fighting the heartbeat. No more ghost dispatches. \nThe system is clean.","timestamp":1780508507876,"idempotencyKey":"279968ef-ae09-4cc4-976c-49f621f75c13:user"}}
{"type":"message","id":"350b2be1","parentId":"5edf215b","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:23:08.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Clean and simple. I've updated MEMORY.md to reflect the final state:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"a61c158e-d533-46a0-9fb9-4b6514116cdc","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md","edits":[{"oldText":"- **2026-06-02:** OPS-002 — Incident→Task Linking: `Task.linkedIncidentId` is source of truth (not `Incident.linkedTaskIds`). Auto-detect creates linked triage tasks. Task status changes auto-append to incident timeline via `/api/incidents/timeline`. Added `triage` to Task status union, new Triage Kanban column, Linked Incident section in task detail, derived linked tasks in IncidentDetailsDrawer.\n\n---\n_Last updated: 2026-06-02 by Space Monkey_","newText":"- **2026-06-02:** OPS-002 — Incident→Task Linking: `Task.linkedIncidentId` is source of truth (not `Incident.linkedTaskIds`). Auto-detect creates linked triage tasks. Task status changes auto-append to incident timeline via `/api/incidents/timeline`. Added `triage` to Task status union, new Triage Kanban column, Linked Incident section in task detail, derived linked tasks in IncidentDetailsDrawer.\n- **2026-06-03:** Task system overhaul — removed work-dispatcher.sh (was flipping JSON without spawning agents). Heartbeat is now the only dispatcher. 28 stale/protected tasks cleaned up (6 incident artifacts → obsolete, 22 strategic → deferred). End-to-end test passed: sub-agent dispatched, completed, moved to Done with summary. 16 planning tasks remain in backlog for human triage.\n\n---\n_Last updated: 2026-06-03 by Space Monkey_"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\": \"- **2026-06-02:** OPS-002 — Incident→Task Linking: `Task.linkedIncidentId` is source of truth (not `Incident.linkedTaskIds`). Auto-detect creates linked triage tasks. Task status changes auto-append to incident timeline via `/api/incidents/timeline`. Added `triage` to Task status union, new Triage Kanban column, Linked Incident section in task detail, derived linked tasks in IncidentDetailsDrawer.\\n\\n---\\n_Last updated: 2026-06-02 by Space Monkey_\", \"newText\": \"- **2026-06-02:** OPS-002 — Incident→Task Linking: `Task.linkedIncidentId` is source of truth (not `Incident.linkedTaskIds`). Auto-detect creates linked triage tasks. Task status changes auto-append to incident timeline via `/api/incidents/timeline`. Added `triage` to Task status union, new Triage Kanban column, Linked Incident section in task detail, derived linked tasks in IncidentDetailsDrawer.\\n- **2026-06-03:** Task system overhaul — removed work-dispatcher.sh (was flipping JSON without spawning agents). Heartbeat is now the only dispatcher. 28 stale/protected tasks cleaned up (6 incident artifacts → obsolete, 22 strategic → deferred). End-to-end test passed: sub-agent dispatched, completed, moved to Done with summary. 16 planning tasks remain in backlog for human triage.\\n\\n---\\n_Last updated: 2026-06-03 by Space Monkey_\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":67346,"output":414,"cacheRead":6784,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":74544,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780508507995,"responseId":"gen-1780508510-j0iCMjHPHRWIsonYBDdZ"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c777cd75","parentId":"350b2be1","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:23:08.223Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"a61c158e-d533-46a0-9fb9-4b6514116cdc","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[... 85 more characters truncated; rerun with narrower args if needed"}],"details":{"diff":"    ...\n 52 - **2026-06-02:** Added `triage` to Task.status union, new Triage Kanban column, Linked Incident section in TaskDetailPanel, `/api/incidents-timeline` endpoint.\n 53 - **2026-06-02:** Updated auto-detect-incidents.sh to create linked tasks + severity-based response actions per incident.\n 54 \n 55 - **2026-06-02:** OPS-002 — Incident→Task Linking: `Task.linkedIncidentId` is source of truth (not `Incident.linkedTaskIds`). Auto-detect creates linked triage tasks. Task status changes auto-append to incident timeline via `/api/incidents/timeline`. Added `triage` to Task status union, new Triage Kanban column, Linked Incident section in task detail, derived linked tasks in IncidentDetailsDrawer.\n+56 - **2026-06-03:** Task system overhaul — removed work-dispatcher.sh (was flipping JSON without spawning agents). Heartbeat is now the only dispatcher. 28 stale/protected tasks cleaned up (6 incident artifacts → obsolete, 22 strategic → deferred). End-to-end test passed: sub-agent dispatched, completed, moved to Done with summary. 16 planning tasks remain in backlog for human triage.\n 56 \n 57 ---\n-58 _Last updated: 2026-06-02 by Space Monkey_\n+59 _Last updated: 2026-06-03 by Space Monkey_","patch":"--- /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md\n+++ /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md\n@@ -52,7 +52,8 @@\n - **2026-06-02:** Added `triage` to Task.status union, new Triage Kanban column, Linked Incident section in TaskDetailPanel, `/api/incidents-timeline` endpoint.\n - **2026-06-02:** Updated auto-detect-incidents.sh to create linked tasks + severity-based response actions per incident.\n \n - **2026-06-02:** OPS-002 — Incident→Task Linking: `Task.linkedIncidentId` is source of truth (not `Incident.linkedTaskIds`). Auto-detect creates linked triage tasks. Task status changes auto-append to incident timeline via `/api/incidents/timeline`. Added `triage` to Task status union, new Triage Kanban column, Linked Incident section in task detail, derived linked tasks in IncidentDetailsDrawer.\n+- **2026-06-03:** Task system overhaul — removed work-dispatcher.sh (was flipping JSON without spawning agents). Heartbeat is now the only dispatcher. 28 stale/protected tasks cleaned up (6 incident artifacts → obsolete, 22 strategic → deferred). End-to-end test passed: sub-agent dispatched, completed, moved to Done with summary. 16 planning tasks remain in backlog for human triage.\n \n ---\n-_Last updated: 2026-06-02 by Space Monkey_\n+_Last updated: 2026-06-03 by Space Monkey_\n","firstChangedLine":56},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780508546272}}
