{"type":"message","id":"7f85feb6","parentId":"9a4f01b9","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:23:08.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Design updated. To summarize the changes:\n\n1. **`nightShiftEligible`** — automatic. System determines eligibility from existing fields (priority, tags, dispatch status). The field only exists as a manual `false` override for edge cases. No manual tagging needed.\n\n2. **Token limit** — bumped to **100K total per night** (~20K avg per task).\n\n3. **Morning report** — now includes station status section: disk usage, overnight incidents, gateway uptime, plus the task summaries.\n\n4. **Dry run** — ready to go whenever you want. No code changes needed. I'll simulate the full logic against the current backlog and log what it WOULD do.\n\nWant me to run the dry run now?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":195,"output":159,"cacheRead":90240,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":90594,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780510336196,"responseId":"gen-1780510336-EafRKOOJiDaNwXGwWuD3"}}
