{"type":"message","id":"9f997aa0","parentId":"a7fc15ed","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:23:08.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Cron created. Now add the Night Shift section to HEARTBEAT.md:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"0f2bbe2a-af97-49d8-be64-655404db7fa8","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## Rule: Sub-agent Timeout","newText":"## Night Shift (01:00-07:00 BST)\n\nAutonomous task processing when Andre is asleep. Design doc: `NIGHT_SHIFT.md`.\n\n### Activation (triggered by cron at 01:00)\nALL conditions must be true:\n- Time is 01:00-07:00 BST\n- Dispatchable backlog tasks exist (see eligibility below)\n- No 429 rate limit errors in last 30 minutes\n- No Andre activity in last 2 hours\n\nIf any condition fails → log reason, skip Night Shift this cycle.\n\n### Task Eligibility\n- `status: \"backlog\"`, no `stalledAt`, `dispatchCount < 3`, not `wasStalled`\n- Priority P2 or P3 only (P1 excluded)\n- No exclusion tags: `needs-human-input`, `planning`, `design`, `roadmap`\n- Sort: P2 before P3, then oldest first\n- **Max 2 tasks tonight** (first night trial — increase after 2 successful nights)\n- No new tasks after 06:30. Hard stop at 07:00.\n- Token limit: 100K total per night\n\n### Dispatch\n- Pick ONE eligible task, spawn sub-agent with full task brief\n- Sub-agent MUST update `currentStep` and `lastActivity` every 5-10 min\n- On completion: mark done with summary, pick next eligible task\n- On failure: move back to backlog with failure note, no retry\n- Stop immediately if 429s detected or Andre sends a message\n\n### Forbidden\n- Never modify openclaw.json, cron jobs, LaunchAgents, or gateway config\n- Never delete tasks — only move to Done with summary\n- Never dispatch P1 tasks\n- Max 5 min per sub-agent (kill if exceeded)\n\n### State\n- Track progress in `data/night-shift-state.json`\n- Archive to `data/night-shift-archive/` after each night\n\n### Morning Report (07:00)\nSend Telegram sitrep:\n```\n🌙 Night Shift Report — [date]\n✅ Completed: X tasks | ⏭️ Skipped: Y | ❌ Failed: Z | 🪙 Tokens: ~N\n\nCompleted:\n• [Task] — [one-line summary]\n\n── Station Status ──\n💾 Disk: workspace X GB / MC repo Y GB\n🚨 Incidents overnight: [count or \"None\"]\n⏱️ Gateway uptime: Xh Ym\n📊 Backlog: N tasks (M night-shift eligible)\n```\n\n## Rule: Sub-agent Timeout"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\": \"## Rule: Sub-agent Timeout\", \"newText\": \"## Night Shift (01:00-07:00 BST)\\n\\nAutonomous task processing when Andre is asleep. Design doc: `NIGHT_SHIFT.md`.\\n\\n### Activation (triggered by cron at 01:00)\\nALL conditions must be true:\\n- Time is 01:00-07:00 BST\\n- Dispatchable backlog tasks exist (see eligibility below)\\n- No 429 rate limit errors in last 30 minutes\\n- No Andre activity in last 2 hours\\n\\nIf any condition fails → log reason, skip Night Shift this cycle.\\n\\n### Task Eligibility\\n- `status: \\\"backlog\\\"`, no `stalledAt`, `dispatchCount < 3`, not `wasStalled`\\n- Priority P2 or P3 only (P1 excluded)\\n- No exclusion tags: `needs-human-input`, `planning`, `design`, `roadmap`\\n- Sort: P2 before P3, then oldest first\\n- **Max 2 tasks tonight** (first night trial — increase after 2 successful nights)\\n- No new tasks after 06:30. Hard stop at 07:00.\\n- Token limit: 100K total per night\\n\\n### Dispatch\\n- Pick ONE eligible task, spawn sub-agent with full task brief\\n- Sub-agent MUST update `currentStep` and `lastActivity` every 5-10 min\\n- On completion: mark done with summary, pick next eligible task\\n- On failure: move back to backlog with failure note, no retry\\n- Stop immediately if 429s detected or Andre sends a message\\n\\n### Forbidden\\n- Never modify openclaw.json, cron jobs, LaunchAgents, or gateway config\\n- Never delete tasks — only move to Done with summary\\n- Never dispatch P1 tasks\\n- Max 5 min per sub-agent (kill if exceeded)\\n\\n### State\\n- Track progress in `data/night-shift-state.json`\\n- Archive to `data/night-shift-archive/` after each night\\n\\n### Morning Report (07:00)\\nSend Telegram sitrep:\\n```\\n🌙 Night Shift Report — [date]\\n✅ Completed: X tasks | ⏭️ Skipped: Y | ❌ Failed: Z | 🪙 Tokens: ~N\\n\\nCompleted:\\n• [Task] — [one-line summary]\\n\\n── Station Status ──\\n💾 Disk: workspace X GB / MC repo Y GB\\n🚨 Incidents overnight: [count or \\\"None\\\"]\\n⏱️ Gateway uptime: Xh Ym\\n📊 Backlog: N tasks (M night-shift eligible)\\n```\\n\\n## Rule: Sub-agent Timeout\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":446,"output":671,"cacheRead":100224,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":101341,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780512210418,"responseId":"gen-1780512210-UBJ38DC40yvfAc4AFvDO"}}
{"type":"message","id":"adf8ff9c","parentId":"9f997aa0","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:23:08.223Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"0f2bbe2a-af97-49d8-be64-655404db7fa8","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[... 88 more characters truncated; rerun with narrower args if needed"}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n  54 - When archiving: append to existing archive, remove from `tasks.json`, commit + push\n  55 - The Done column should always show recent completions (last 30 days minimum)\n  56 - Archive is for long-term storage only — the Kanban is the source of truth\n  57 \n+ 58 ## Night Shift (01:00-07:00 BST)\n+ 59 \n+ 60 Autonomous task processing when Andre is asleep. Design doc: `NIGHT_SHIFT.md`.\n+ 61 \n+ 62 ### Activation (triggered by cron at 01:00)\n+ 63 ALL conditions must be true:\n+ 64 - Time is 01:00-07:00 BST\n+ 65 - Dispatchable backlog tasks exist (see eligibility below)\n+ 66 - No 429 rate limit errors in last 30 minutes\n+ 67 - No Andre activity in last 2 hours\n+ 68 \n+ 69 If any condition fails → log reason, skip Night Shift this cycle.\n+ 70 \n+ 71 ### Task Eligibility\n+ 72 - `status: \"backlog\"`, no `stalledAt`, `dispatchCount < 3`, not `wasStalled`\n+ 73 - Priority P2 or P3 only (P1 excluded)\n+ 74 - No exclusion tags: `needs-human-input`, `planning`, `design`, `roadmap`\n+ 75 - Sort: P2 before P3, then oldest first\n+ 76 - **Max 2 tasks tonight** (first night trial — increase after 2 successful nights)\n+ 77 - No new tasks after 06:30. Hard stop at 07:00.\n+ 78 - Token limit: 100K total per night\n+ 79 \n+ 80 ### Dispatch\n+ 81 - Pick ONE eligible task, spawn sub-agent with full task brief\n+ 82 - Sub-agent MUST update `currentStep` and `lastActivity` every 5-10 min\n+ 83 - On completion: mark done with summary, pick next eligible task\n+ 84 - On failure: move back to backlog with failure note, no retry\n+ 85 - Stop immediately if 429s detected or Andre sends a message\n+ 86 \n+ 87 ### Forbidden\n+ 88 - Never modify openclaw.json, cron jobs, LaunchAgents, or gateway config\n+ 89 - Never delete tasks — only move to Done with summary\n+ 90 - Never dispatch P1 tasks\n+ 91 - Max 5 min per sub-agent (kill if exceeded)\n+ 92 \n+ 93 ### State\n+ 94 - Track progress in `data/night-shift-state.json`\n+ 95 - Archive to `data/night-shift-archive/` after each night\n+ 96 \n+ 97 ### Morning Report (07:00)\n+ 98 Send Telegram sitrep:\n+ 99 ```\n+100 🌙 Night Shift Report — [date]\n+101 ✅ Completed: X tasks | ⏭️ Skipped: Y | ❌ Failed: Z | 🪙 Tokens: ~N\n+102 \n+103 Completed:\n+104 • [Task] — [one-line summary]\n+105 \n+106 ── Station Status ──\n+107 💾 Disk: workspace X GB / MC repo Y GB\n+108 🚨 Incidents overnight: [count or \"None\"]\n+109 ⏱️ Gateway uptime: Xh Ym\n+110 📊 Backlog: N tasks (M night-shift eligible)\n+111 ```\n+112 \n  58 ## Rule: Sub-agent Timeout\n  59 - If a sub-agent runs for >5 minutes with no resolution, kill it and add the task to backlog\n  60 - If the main agent spends >10 minutes debugging the same issue, stop and add to backlog\n  61 - Always report what was tried and what the blocker is when adding to backlog","patch":"--- /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\n+++ /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\n@@ -54,8 +54,63 @@\n - When archiving: append to existing archive, remove from `tasks.json`, commit + push\n - The Done column should always show recent completions (last 30 days minimum)\n - Archive is for long-term storage only — the Kanban is the source of truth\n \n+## Night Shift (01:00-07:00 BST)\n+\n+Autonomous task processing when Andre is asleep. Design doc: `NIGHT_SHIFT.md`.\n+\n+### Activation (triggered by cron at 01:00)\n+ALL conditions must be true:\n+- Time is 01:00-07:00 BST\n+- Dispatchable backlog tasks exist (see eligibility below)\n+- No 429 rate limit errors in last 30 minutes\n+- No Andre activity in last 2 hours\n+\n+If any condition fails → log reason, skip Night Shift this cycle.\n+\n+### Task Eligibility\n+- `status: \"backlog\"`, no `stalledAt`, `dispatchCount < 3`, not `wasStalled`\n+- Priority P2 or P3 only (P1 excluded)\n+- No exclusion tags: `needs-human-input`, `planning`, `design`, `roadmap`\n+- Sort: P2 before P3, then oldest first\n+- **Max 2 tasks tonight** (first night trial — increase after 2 successful nights)\n+- No new tasks after 06:30. Hard stop at 07:00.\n+- Token limit: 100K total per night\n+\n+### Dispatch\n+- Pick ONE eligible task, spawn sub-agent with full task brief\n+- Sub-agent MUST update `currentStep` and `lastActivity` every 5-10 min\n+- On completion: mark done with summary, pick next eligible task\n+- On failure: move back to backlog with failure note, no retry\n+- Stop immediately if 429s detected or Andre sends a message\n+\n+### Forbidden\n+- Never modify openclaw.json, cron jobs, LaunchAgents, or gateway config\n+- Never delete tasks — only move to Done with summary\n+- Never dispatch P1 tasks\n+- Max 5 min per sub-agent (kill if exceeded)\n+\n+### State\n+- Track progress in `data/night-shift-state.json`\n+- Archive to `data/night-shift-archive/` after each night\n+\n+### Morning Report (07:00)\n+Send Telegram sitrep:\n+```\n+🌙 Night Shift Report — [date]\n+✅ Completed: X tasks | ⏭️ Skipped: Y | ❌ Failed: Z | 🪙 Tokens: ~N\n+\n+Completed:\n+• [Task] — [one-line summary]\n+\n+── Station Status ──\n+💾 Disk: workspace X GB / MC repo Y GB\n+🚨 Incidents overnight: [count or \"None\"]\n+⏱️ Gateway uptime: Xh Ym\n+📊 Backlog: N tasks (M night-shift eligible)\n+```\n+\n ## Rule: Sub-agent Timeout\n - If a sub-agent runs for >5 minutes with no resolution, kill it and add the task to backlog\n - If the main agent spends >10 minutes debugging the same issue, stop and add to backlog\n - Always report what was tried and what the blocker is when adding to backlog\n","firstChangedLine":58},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780512233026}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d76470e","parentId":"adf8ff9c","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:23:08.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now create the night-shift-state.json for tonight:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"0cf89a9d-62c5-4859-8c06-68584a21f7bc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\n\nnow = datetime.now(timezone.utc)\n\nstate = {\n    \"active\": False,\n    \"date\": now.strftime('%Y-%m-%d'),\n    \"startedAt\": None,\n    \"tasksCompleted\": [],\n    \"tasksAttempted\": 0,\n    \"tasksFailed\": [],\n    \"tokensUsed\": 0,\n    \"currentTask\": None,\n    \"stoppedReason\": None,\n    \"maxTasks\": 2,\n    \"note\": \"First night trial — max 2 tasks\"\n}\n\nwith open('/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/data/night-shift-state.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(state, f, indent=2)\n\nprint(f\"Created night-shift-state.json for {state['date']}\")\nprint(f\"Max tasks: {state['maxTasks']}\")\nPYEOF","timeout":5},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"python3 << 'PYEOF'\\nimport json\\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\\n\\nnow = datetime.now(timezone.utc)\\n\\nstate = {\\n    \\\"active\\\": False,\\n    \\\"date\\\": now.strftime('%Y-%m-%d'),\\n    \\\"startedAt\\\": None,\\n    \\\"tasksCompleted\\\": [],\\n    \\\"tasksAttempted\\\": 0,\\n    \\\"tasksFailed\\\": [],\\n    \\\"tokensUsed\\\": 0,\\n    \\\"currentTask\\\": None,\\n    \\\"stoppedReason\\\": None,\\n    \\\"maxTasks\\\": 2,\\n    \\\"note\\\": \\\"First night trial — max 2 tasks\\\"\\n}\\n\\nwith open('/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/data/night-shift-state.json', 'w') as f:\\n    json.dump(state, f, indent=2)\\n\\nprint(f\\\"Created night-shift-state.json for {state['date']}\\\")\\nprint(f\\\"Max tasks: {state['maxTasks']}\\\")\\nPYEOF\", \"timeout\": 5}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":771,"output":220,"cacheRead":100608,"cac