{"type":"message","id":"6d402bfb-aed5-4a14-9587-48a202d9fa56","parentId":"476a158d","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:30:18.950Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"Good work on Automation Health States and Retry Policies. \n\nFor the remaining backlog: Incident Response Atmosphere was being \nbuilt last night — what's the status? Is it complete or partially done?\n\nIf it's done: pick up Operational Readiness Dashboard (P2).\nIf it's still in progress: finish it first, then Operational Readiness.\n\nSkip Runbook Evolution — it's blocked until Phase 2 Runbooks exists.\n\nAlso: \"Operational Readiness Dashboard\" keeps getting picked up and \ngoing stale (140min, then 30min). Before working on it, check why \nthe sub-agent isn't actually starting work after dispatch. Is the \ntask too vague, or is the dispatch process failing silently?","timestamp":1780525722115,"idempotencyKey":"ddba60ff-51c8-4e14-bcb6-ebe57eb23e60:user"}}
