 implemented: (a) AmbientStation tint shift wired to incident severity (P1→critical/red, P2→alert/amber, P3/P4→busy/warm, none→calm), (b) Alert banner on Dashboard when incidents open (⚠️ N open incidents — clickable to Incidents page), (c) Room pulse for assigned agent — StationFloorplan activeIncidentRooms prop adds subtle glow to rooms where incident owners are assigned. Build verified clean.'\\n        t['lastActivity'] = now.isoformat()\\n        if 'history' not in t:\\n            t['history'] = []\\n        t['history'].append({\\n            'ts': now.isoformat(),\\n            'action': 'updated',\\n            'actor': 'monkey',\\n            'details': 'Room pulse effect completed — StationFloorplan activeIncidentRooms prop + Dashboard wiring'\\n        })\\n        print(f\\\"✅ Updated: {t['title']}\\\")\\n        break\\n\\nwith open(tasks_file, 'w') as f:\\n    json.dump(tasks, f, indent=2)\\nPYEOF\", \"timeout\": 5}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":517,"output":357,"cacheRead":58240,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":59114,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780526030284,"responseId":"gen-1780526030-l5FfVSLQQqCHH9azgACp"}}
