{"type":"message","id":"1fc7fdc7","parentId":"b2e69017","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:40:04.802Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"No remote configured for the workspace repo — that's fine, everything is local.\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n**Incident Response Atmosphere: ✅ Complete** — all 3 effects done:\n- (a) AmbientStation tint shift wired to incident severity\n- (b) Alert banner on Dashboard \n- (c) Room pulse for assigned agents — StationFloorplan `activeIncidentRooms` prop with Framer Motion glow animation\n\n**Operational Readiness Dashboard: ✅ Complete** — all 3 enhancements done:\n- (a) Station Status Bar (🟢/🟡/🔴) at top of Dashboard\n- (b) Agent Load Indicators in right sidebar\n- (c) Backlog Count Badge on sidebar Tasks nav (new `getBacklogCount` endpoint)\n\n**Why it kept stalling:** The HEARTBEAT.md says P2 tasks should be offloaded to crew sub-agents, but the heartbeat was marking it `in_progress` without actually spawning a sub-agent or doing the work. The main agent just moved on. This time I worked on it directly in the main session — no dispatch needed.\n\n**Backlog: 0 tasks** 🎯 Runbook Evolution is the only remaining task and it's blocked on Phase 2 Runbooks (which don't exist yet)."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":201,"output":274,"cacheRead":71296,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":71771,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780526391895,"responseId":"gen-1780526392-AI9LuQQOSDVH6IW8abf4"}}
