{"type":"message","id":"22e233fd","parentId":"298f94d6","timestamp":"2026-06-03T23:22:38.371Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now set up the daily auto-resolve cron. I'll add it as a cron job that runs the auto-resolve endpoint:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ec458588-781a-40c5-8322-9ae2ed2019dd","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"Daily Incident Auto-Resolve","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 6 * * *","tz":"Europe/London"},"payload":{"kind":"systemEvent","text":"⏰ Daily Incident Auto-Resolve cron fired.\n\nRun the auto-resolve endpoint to clean up stale incidents:\n1. POST to /api/incidents/auto-resolve with { closeOldDays: 5 }\n2. This resolves incidents whose linked tasks are done\n3. This closes incidents with no linked tasks that are 5+ days old\n4. Log the results\n\nThis prevents the incident graveyard from building up again. The endpoint is at /api/incidents/auto-resolve — it reads incidents.json and tasks.json, resolves/closes stale entries, and writes back."},"sessionTarget":"main","enabled":true}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"add\", \"job\": {\"name\": \"Daily Incident Auto-Resolve\", \"schedule\": {\"kind\": \"cron\", \"expr\": \"0 6 * * *\", \"tz\": \"Europe/London\"}, \"payload\": {\"kind\": \"systemEvent\", \"text\": \"⏰ Daily Incident Auto-Resolve cron fired.\\n\\nRun the auto-resolve endpoint to clean up stale incidents:\\n1. POST to /api/incidents/auto-resolve with { closeOldDays: 5 }\\n2. This resolves incidents whose linked tasks are done\\n3. This closes incidents with no linked tasks that are 5+ days old\\n4. Log the results\\n\\nThis prevents the incident graveyard from building up again. The endpoint is at /api/incidents/auto-resolve — it reads incidents.json and tasks.json, resolves/closes stale entries, and writes back.\"}, \"sessionTarget\": \"main\", \"enabled\": true}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":557,"output":238,"cacheRead":99328,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":100123,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780528946443,"responseId":"gen-1780528946-0e9VbvN0DpzYFpbaEEiN"}}
