{"type":"message","id":"ca4afa40","parentId":"d142a624","timestamp":"2026-06-03T23:22:51.939Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ace3188c-d3d6-4eaa-9a01-aebc1b263711","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"⏱️ Gateway uptime: Xh Ym\n📊 Backlog: N tasks (M night-shift eligible)\n```\n\n**Progress update assessment:** For each completed task, check its history. If there are no `progress` or `step_update` entries between `started` and `completed`, flag it. The goal is at least 2-3 intermediate updates per task.\n\n## Rule: Sub-agent Timeout\n- If a sub-agent runs for >5 minutes with no resolution, kill it and add the task to backlog\n- If the main agent spends >10 minutes debugging the same issue, stop and add to backlog\n- Always report what was tried and what the blocker is when adding to backlog\n\n[1 more lines in file. Use offset=130 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780528971939}}
{"type":"message","id":"db9aba45","parentId":"ca4afa40","timestamp":"2026-06-03T23:23:11.120Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"b79c8675-b822-47ae-b3b7-560d7148b862","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## Rule: Sub-agent Timeout","newText":"## IncidentAuto-Resolve (check EVERY heartbeat)\n- Read `data/incidents.json`, count open (non-RESOLVED) incidents\n- If open incidents > 10: run auto-resolve\n  - POST to `/api/incidents/auto-resolve` with `{ closeOldDays: 5 }`\n  - This endpoint resolves incidents whose linked tasks are done and closes old orphans\n  - If the endpoint doesn't exist yet, run the equivalent Python script directly:\n    ```python\n    # See /api/incidents/auto-resolve.tsx for logic\n    # Resolve: linked task done → incident RESOLVED\n    # Close: no linked task AND age >= 5 days → RESOLVED\n    ```\n- This prevents the incident graveyard from building up again\n- The daily 6 AM cron does this automatically; heartbeat is a safety net\n\n## Rule: Sub-agent Timeout"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\": \"## Rule: Sub-agent Timeout\", \"newText\": \"## IncidentAuto-Resolve (check EVERY heartbeat)\\n- Read `data/incidents.json`, count open (non-RESOLVED) incidents\\n- If open incidents > 10: run auto-resolve\\n  - POST to `/api/incidents/auto-resolve` with `{ closeOldDays: 5 }`\\n  - This endpoint resolves incidents whose linked tasks are done and closes old orphans\\n  - If the endpoint doesn't exist yet, run the equivalent Python script directly:\\n    ```python\\n    # See /api/incidents/auto-resolve.tsx for logic\\n    # Resolve: linked task done → incident RESOLVED\\n    # Close: no linked task AND age >= 5 days → RESOLVED\\n    ```\\n- This prevents the incident graveyard from building up again\\n- The daily 6 AM cron does this automatically; heartbeat is a safety net\\n\\n## Rule: Sub-agent Timeout\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":239,"output":250,"cacheRead":100608,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":101097,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780528971954,"responseId":"gen-1780528972-DFDNXp8dqQI6ET9HqCeY"}}
