{"type":"message","id":"0a9a9160","parentId":"56edb687","timestamp":"2026-06-03T23:24:40.045Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Summary\n\n**All 3 remaining TRIAGE incidents now have linked tasks:**\n- INC-039 (P1 gateway crash-loop) → `task-inc-039-42f8` (triage)\n- INC-038 (P3 stale tasks) → `task-inc-038-7679` (triage)\n- INC-036 (P2 rate limit) → `task-inc-036-b8c2` (triage)\n\n**Root cause fixed:** The auto-detect script's dedup logic was `exit(0)` when it found an existing TRIAGE incident with the same title+source — skipping task creation entirely. Now it checks: if the incident exists but has no linked task, it creates one. If the incident exists and already has a linked task, it skips.\n\n**Auto-resolve safety net:**\n- **Daily cron at 6 AM BST** — runs `/api/incidents/auto-resolve` automatically\n- **Heartbeat check** — if open incidents > 10, triggers auto-resolve immediately\n- The endpoint resolves incidents whose linked tasks are done, and closes orphans ≥ 5 days old\n\n**Board state:** 39 RESOLVED, 3 TRIAGE (all with linked tasks), 0 ghosts. MC 200."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":147,"output":289,"cacheRead":102912,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":103348,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780529063594,"responseId":"gen-1780529063-wJC96n4Qnm7rkIo11l06"}}
