{"type":"message","id":"5a3e99f6","parentId":"1f0226b9","timestamp":"2026-06-03T23:44:02.047Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Triple guard now: tag exclusion + `wasStalled` + `dispatchCount >= 3`. This task will never be ghost-dispatched again.\n\n**Heartbeat Report:**\n- **MC:** ✅ 200\n- **Tasks:** 2 done, 5 triage (incident-linked), 1 backlog (Runbook Evolution — now properly blocked)\n- **Incidents:** 39 RESOLVED, 5 TRIAGE — all 5 have linked tasks ✅\n- **Fixed:** Heartbeat exclusion tag filter (phase-2-dependent etc.) + Runbook Evolution triple-guarded against re-dispatch\n- **New incidents:** INC-044 (P1 gateway), INC-043 (P2 WD mount) — auto-detect is working correctly with the dedup fix\n\nHEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":267,"output":176,"cacheRead":105984,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":106427,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780530232855,"responseId":"gen-1780530233-umkOPrjdjbnSn16noYT4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"552059fa","parentId":"5a3e99f6","timestamp":"2026-06-03T23:48:15.332Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"Mission: External AI Review Loop (Phase 1 Validation)\n\nObjective\n\nI want to test whether external AI review improves the quality of OpenClaw’s work before investing time in automation.\n\nThe long-term goal is:\n\nOpenClaw completes work\n→ Review package generated\n→ External AI reviews work\n→ Recommendations returned\n→ OpenClaw evaluates recommendations\n→ Accepted improvements implemented\n→ Repeat\n\nPhase 1 is framework only.\n\nNo browser automation.\nNo external API integrations.\nNo DeepSeek, ChatGPT or Claude connections yet.\n\nThe objective is to create the process and artefacts needed to test the workflow manually.\n\n⸻\n\nDeliverables\n\nCreate:\n\n~/.openclaw/workspace/review-system/\n├── pending/\n├── reviewed/\n├── recommendations/\n├── templates/\n├── logs/\n├── review-agent/\n└── README.md\n\n⸻\n\nTemplates\n\nCreate the following templates.\n\nreview-package.md\n\n---\nreview_id:\nproject:\ncreated:\npriority:\nstatus:\n---\n# Summary\nWhat was completed.\n# Files Changed\nList affected files.\n# Decisions Made\nDecision:\nReason:\n# Risks Identified\nPotential risks.\n# Known Limitations\nCurrent limitations.\n# Proposed Next Steps\nPlanned work.\n# Questions For Reviewer\nSpecific questions where external critique would be valuable.\n\nrecommendation.md\n\n---\nreview_id:\nreviewer:\nreceived:\n---\n# Recommendations\n## Recommendation\nPriority:\nReasoning:\nExpected Benefit:\n\ndecision-log.md\n\n---\nreview_id:\nrecommendation:\noutcome:\nreason:\naction:\n---\n\n⸻\n\nReview Triggers\n\nGenerate review packages when:\n\n* Feature completed\n* Significant refactor completed\n* Architectural change made\n* Infrastructure change made\n* Security change made\n\nDo NOT generate review packages for:\n\n* Small bug fixes\n* Documentation updates\n* Minor UI changes\n* Routine maintenance\n\n⸻\n\nReview Agent (Design Only)\n\nCreate a documented review-agent design.\n\nResponsibilities:\n\n1. Detect completed work requiring review.\n2. Generate review packages.\n3. Track review status.\n\nStates:\n\npending\n→ in-review\n→ reviewed\n→ actioned\n→ archived\n\n4. Accept reviewer recommendations.\n5. Record decisions:\n    * Accepted\n    * Rejected\n    * Deferred\n6. Record reasoning for every decision.\n7. Maintain audit history.\n\nDo not implement automation.\n\nDocument the future implementation plan.\n\n⸻\n\nPhase 2 Investigation\n\nEvaluate three future integration options.\n\nOption A: Browser Automation\n\nOpenClaw uses browser tooling to submit review packages to DeepSeek, ChatGPT or Claude.\n\nEvaluate:\n\n* implementation complexity\n* reliability\n* maintenance burden\n* operational risks\n* scalability\n\nOption B: OpenRouter Reviewer\n\nOpenClaw submits review packages through OpenRouter using a dedicated reviewer model.\n\nEvaluate:\n\n* implementation complexity\n* reliability\n* maintenance burden\n* operational risks\n* scalability\n* estimated cost\n\nOption C: Dedicated Reviewer Account\n\nOpenClaw submits review packages to a dedicated DeepSeek or Claude API account used solely for review.\n\nEvaluate:\n\n* implementation complexity\n* reliability\n* maintenance burden\n* operational risks\n* scalability\n* estimated cost\n\nCreate a comparison matrix.\n\nRecommend a preferred Phase 2 approach.\n\n⸻\n\nFirst Review Package\n\nCreate:\n\npending/REV-2026-06-04-001.md\n\nSummarise:\n\nMission Control Agent Office\n\n* Canvas sprite crew system\n* Crew visits\n* Mood lighting\n\nScheduler\n\n* Automation Health States\n* Retry Policies\n\nIncident Management\n\n* Incident cleanup from 39 to 3\n* Auto-resolution fixes\n\nTriage\n\n* Seven tasks clarified and actioned\n\nOperations Engine\n\n* Backlog processing\n* Stall detection\n* Ghost dispatch fix\n\nCurrent State\n\n* Board clear\n* Zero backlog\n* Station stable\n\nInclude:\n\n1. Key decisions made.\n2. Risks still remaining.\n3. Areas where external review could add value.\n4. Specific reviewer questions.\n\n⸻\n\nSuccess Criteria\n\nA successful Phase 1 implementation provides:\n\n* Review system directory structure\n* Working templates\n* Review workflow\n* Review-agent design\n* Architecture comparison\n* First review package\n\nAt the end provide:\n\n1. Whether the review process is likely to improve outcomes.\n2. Whether Phase 2 automation is justified.\n3. Which integration option should be implemented first.\n4. A phased roadmap from manual review to automated external AI review.\n\n:::\nThis will give you something concrete to test:\n```text\nSpace Monkey finishes work\n        ↓\nCreates review package\n        ↓\nYou paste review package here\n        ↓\nI review it\n        ↓\nRecommendations saved\n        ↓\nYou give recommendations back to Space Monkey\n\nIf after a few cycles you find the recommendations are genuinely improving the work, then the next prompt is not “build a review board”, it’s:\n\n“Implement Phase 2 using the recommended integration method and automate the review package → reviewer → recommendation pipeline.”\n\nThat way you’re validating value before building automation.","timestamp":1780530495167,"idempotencyKey":"82bdfbb6-2199-445b-854f-2f7c637fba03:user"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9dd8dc74","parentId":"552059fa","timestamp":"2026-06-03T23:48:27.435Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nThis is a well-structured mission. Let me break it down and execute."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"8b6b6a87-42ea-42c0-86f1-4ea77db714d3","name":"update_plan","arguments":{"plan":[{"step":"Create review-system directory structure","status":"in_progress"},{"step":"Create templates (review-package, recommendation, decision-log)","status":"pending"},{"step":"Create review-agent design document","status":"pending"},{"step":"Create Phase 2 comparison matrix","status":"pending"},{"step":"Create first review package REV-2026-06-04-001","status":"pending"},{"step":"Write README.md with success criteria and roadmap","status":"pending"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"plan\": [{\"step\": \"Create review-system directory structure\", \"status\": \"in_progress\"}, {\"step\": \"Create templates (review-package, recommendation, decision-log)\", \"status\": \"pending\"}, {\"step\": \"Create review-agent design document\", \"status\": \"pending\"}, {\"step\": \"Create Phase 2 comparison matrix\", \"status\": \"pending\"}, {\"step\": \"Create first review package REV-2026-06-04-001\", \"status\": \"pending\"}, {\"step\": \"Write README.md with success criteria and roadmap\", \"status\": \"pending\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":98181,"output":153,"cacheRead":9600,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":107934,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780530495342,"responseId":"gen-1780530495-T1PNLp8cytYrb05S4cmd"}}
