{"type":"message","id":"314d0052","parentId":"8e7caebf","timestamp":"2026-06-03T23:52:59.259Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"0e3ccc4a-d569-4a6d-a01c-12ff18b765e8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && git add review-system/ data/tasks.json && git commit -m \"External AI Review Loop — Phase 1 framework\n\n- Directory structure: pending/, reviewed/, recommendations/, templates/, logs/, review-agent/\n- Templates: review-package.md, recommendation.md, decision-log.md\n- Review Agent design: responsibilities, state machine, workflow\n- Phase 2 analysis: Browser vs OpenRouter vs Dedicated API comparison\n  → Recommendation: OpenRouter (provider-agnostic, low maintenance, ~$100/mo)\n- First review package: REV-2026-06-04-001 (full session summary)\n- README: success criteria, assessment, phased roadmap\n- Task: task-review-system created\"","timeout":10},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && git add review-system/ data/tasks.json && git commit -m \\\"External AI Review Loop — Phase 1 framework\\n\\n- Directory structure: pending/, reviewed/, recommendations/, templates/, logs/, review-agent/\\n- Templates: review-package.md, recommendation.md, decision-log.md\\n- Review Agent design: responsibilities, state machine, workflow\\n- Phase 2 analysis: Browser vs OpenRouter vs Dedicated API comparison\\n  → Recommendation: OpenRouter (provider-agnostic, low maintenance, ~$100/mo)\\n- First review package: REV-2026-06-04-001 (full session summary)\\n- README: success criteria, assessment, phased roadmap\\n- Task: task-review-system created\\\"\", \"timeout\": 10}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":260,"output":184,"cacheRead":114560,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":115004,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780530769024,"responseId":"gen-1780530